{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"CSS 选择器","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/CSS_Selector","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><strong>CSS 选择器</strong>是 CSS 规则的一部分，用于匹配文档中的元素。匹配的元素将会应用规则指定的样式。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"示例","title":"示例","isH3":false,"content":"<p>看下面的 CSS：</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: css notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token selector\">p</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> green<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token selector\">div.warning</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">width</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 100%<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">border</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 2px solid yellow<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> white<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">background-color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> darkred<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">padding</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 0.8em 0.8em 0.6em<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token selector\">#customized</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">font</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 16px Lucida Grande<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> Arial<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> Helvetica<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> sans-serif<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>选择器例如：<code>\"p\"</code>（文档中的 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/p\"><code>&lt;p&gt;</code></a> 元素都会应用绿色字体的样式）、<code>\"div.warning\"</code>（文档中所有 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Global_attributes/class\">class</a> 包含 <code>\"warning\"</code> 的 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/div\"><code>&lt;div&gt;</code></a> 元素都会有一个看起来像警告框的样式）和 <code>\"#customized\"</code>（id 为 <code>\"customized\"</code> 的元素中的文本为 16px 高，字体是 Lucida Grande 和一些用作回落的字体）。</p>\n<p>我们可以把上面的 CSS 应用到 HTML 中，如下：</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>This is happy text.<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>warning<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  Be careful! There are wizards present, and they are quick to anger!\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">id</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>customized<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>This is happy text.<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>warning<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    Be careful! There are wizards present, and they are quick to anger!\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>页面的内容将会呈现如下样式：</p><iframe class=\"sample-code-frame\" title=\"示例 sample\" id=\"frame_示例\" width=\"640\" height=\"240\" src=\"https://yari-demos.prod.mdn.mozit.cloud/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/CSS_Selector/_sample_.%E7%A4%BA%E4%BE%8B.html\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"参见","title":"参见","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li>查看我们的关于选择器的介绍 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Learn/CSS/Building_blocks/Selectors\">CSS 选择器</a></li>\n  <li>基础选择器\n    <ul>\n      <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/Type_selectors\">标签选择器</a> <code>elementname</code></li>\n      <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/Class_selectors\">类选择器</a> <code>.classname</code></li>\n      <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/ID_selectors\">ID 选择器</a> <code>#idname</code></li>\n      <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/Universal_selectors\">通配选择器</a> <code>* ns|* *|*</code></li>\n      <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/Attribute_selectors\">属性选择器</a> <code>[attr=value]</code></li>\n      <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/Pseudo-classes\">状态选择器</a> <code>a:active, a:visited</code></li>\n    </ul>\n  </li>\n  <li>组选择器\n    <ul>\n      <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/Selector_list\">选择器列表</a> <code>A, B</code></li>\n    </ul>\n  </li>\n  <li>关系选择器\n    <ul>\n      <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/Adjacent_sibling_combinator\">邻近兄弟元素选择器</a> <code>A + B</code></li>\n      <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/General_sibling_combinator\">兄弟元素选择器</a> <code>A ~ B</code></li>\n      <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/Child_combinator\">直接子元素选择器</a> <code>A &gt; B</code></li>\n      <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/Descendant_combinator\">后代元素选择器</a> <code>A B</code></li>\n    </ul>\n  </li>\n  <li>伪选择器（Pseudo）\n    <ul>\n      <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/Pseudo-classes\">伪类</a> <code>:</code></li>\n      <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/Pseudo-elements\">伪元素</a> <code>::</code></li>\n    </ul>\n  </li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"示例","id":"示例"},{"text":"参见","id":"参见"}],"summary":"CSS 选择器是 CSS 规则的一部分，用于匹配文档中的元素。匹配的元素将会应用规则指定的样式。","popularity":0.0002,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Selector (CSS)","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Sélecteur CSS","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Selector (セレクター (CSS) )","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Selector (CSS)","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"CSS-селектор","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"CSS 選擇器","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/glossary/css_selector","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/glossary/css_selector/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary","title":"术语表"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/CSS_Selector","title":"CSS 选择器"}],"pageTitle":"CSS 选择器 - 术语表 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}